# Layer-Stage Framework - Cursor Rules

## Context
This is the universal root (Layer 0) of the Layer-Stage Framework.

## Navigation
- layer_0/ contains universal framework internals
- layer_1/ contains projects, features, components

## Naming Conventions
- Directories: layer_N_XX_name (underscores, not dots)
- Sub-layers: sub_layer_N_XX_name
- Stages: stage_N_XX_name

## When Working Here
- Check CLAUDE.md for context
- Check layer_0/layer_0_00_ai_manager_system/agnostic/ for init prompts
- Follow the entity pattern for all new content
